<bibl>
                        <ref target="#uuid-8d17a8f3-d898-45e5-a63a-896350e61c19">JINGDECHUANDENGLU</ref>
<title>景德傳燈錄 Jǐngdé chuándēng lù The Record of the Transmission of the Lamp Published in the Jǐngdé Era Taishō</title>
                        <biblScope unit="page">258b</biblScope>
                        <note>
<p>陸異日又謂師曰。弟子亦薄會佛法。師便問大夫十二時中作麼生。陸云。寸絲不掛。師云。猶是階下漢。</p>
                        </note>
                    </bibl>
<bibl>
                        <ref target="#uuid-8d17a8f3-d898-45e5-a63a-896350e61c19">JINGDECHUANDENGLU</ref>
<title>景德傳燈錄 Jǐngdé chuándēng lù The Record of the Transmission of the Lamp Published in the Jǐngdé Era Taishō</title>
                        <biblScope unit="page">304c</biblScope>
                        <note>
<p>僧問。如何是和尚不欺人眼。師曰。看看冬到來。僧曰。究竟如何。師曰。即便春風至。問遠聞和尚6寸絲7不掛。及至到來為什麼有山可守。師曰。道什麼。僧喝。師亦喝。僧禮拜。</p>
                        </note>
                    </bibl>
                </listBibl>
